dct_title_s: Aus Africa holt man oele, wolle, leder, wachs, gold, kupfer, helfenbein, schwarze sclaven
dct_description_sm: Latitudinal and longitudinal lines around margins.
Coordinates are approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Shows drainage, boundaries, natual resources, including minerals, fiber and "schwarze sclaven."
